Name: Basic Bifra Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Runestone, Wisdom 13 Or Greater
Description: This rune symbolizes the bridge between realms, a path from the divine to mortalkind, allowing those who channel it to tap into the power of translocation.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACEBridge StepSPACEAs an action, you can teleport to an unoccupied space you can see within DISTANCE10-20DISTANCE feet of you.SPACESPACEYou may use this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest. This rune occupies 1 runic attunement slot.
